<br>
When it comes down to it, I feel that rangers are a ranged class.  Why in the hell would you call them rangers if they're up there with hugs swords/axes?<br>
<br>
My thought is rangers are used with Bows and Trueshot and such.  A ranger up in melee combat is ok, so long as he/she uses Jolt, and controls his/her agro.<br>
<br>
What is the consensus about this (God I hate that word)? <p><center>
